WEBVTT

1
00:24:35.050 --> 00:24:37.470 
这个莫扎特 他有多好？
How good is he, this Mozart?

2
00:24:37.680 --> 00:24:39.570 
陛下 他太让人惊讶了
He's remarkable, Majesty.

3
00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:43.270 
我上个月去听了一出他作的正歌剧
I heard an extraordinary serious opera of his last month.

4
00:24:43.520 --> 00:24:46.900 
-《克里特王依多美尼欧》    -就它？
- Idomeneo, King of Crete.  - That?

5
00:24:47.690 --> 00:24:50.230 
一部无聊的作品 我也听过
A tiresome piece. I heard it too.

6
00:24:50.900 --> 00:24:52.150 
无聊？
Tiresome?

7
00:24:53.070 --> 00:24:57.360 
一个年轻人班门弄斧而已
A young man trying to impress beyond his abilities.

8
00:24:57.570 --> 00:25:02.290 
太多加料 太多音符了
Too much spice. Too em... too many notes.

9
00:25:02.910 --> 00:25:07.920 
陛下 我认为这是我近些年来听到的最好的作品
Majesty, I thought it was the most promising work I've heard in years.

